{"tid":1784432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警員旺角驅散聚集市民　無警告下施放胡椒噴霧","createTime":"2019-12-15T16:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T16:33:43.000Z","uid":7828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e2ca3559826805f8f7b381ace76c2f26069891d","tid":1784432,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:07:50.000Z","msg":"旺角晚上有市民聚集，防暴警員到場，施放胡椒噴霧驅散，帶走至少兩人。<br />\n<br />\n旺角朗豪坊對出砵蘭街晚上有市民聚集，防暴警察到場驅散，期間截查多人，引起市民不滿。有警員在無警告下，突然施放胡椒噴霧，行經的路人即時閃避，警員至少帶走兩人上警車。<br />\n<br />\n到晚上近十時半，防暴警員沿彌敦道行人路向油麻地方向推進，在場有市民大叫有小朋友跌倒，但警察無理會繼續推前，又指罵記者是「黑記」。<br />\n<br />\n另外在晚上十時許，將軍澳尚德邨對開的十字路口有人在路邊掘磚頭，將磚頭拋出馬路，又打爛附近的交通燈，用單車等雜物做路障，堵塞了附近一段車路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=373475&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D373475%26refer%3DShare&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=1eace06e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D373475%26refer%3DShare&h=a7fdd5c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=373475&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"b97d42bad8ba1773dadfa227e88233f0826300d8","tid":1784432,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實要停聖誕消費借黑警手係咪易過借火，一堆人唱吓歌都發癲"},{"pid":"f6f31c3d465377cbb524795e07467b9555a14974","tid":1784432,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b97d42bad8ba1773dadfa227e88233f0826300d8","tid":1784432,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實要停聖誕消費借黑警手係咪易過借火，一堆人唱吓歌都發癲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"過年了，要出番多D 加班費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebf4bacf51c732659783d1b44beed2d38c80f0f","tid":1784432,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"好多香港人仲諗住 聖誕出黎玩，快D幫手整到佢地無得去玩"},{"pid":"99f51ef01b7e67befece32fc50c954226cfbbb3f","tid":1784432,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6f31c3d465377cbb524795e07467b9555a14974","tid":1784432,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b97d42bad8ba1773dadfa227e88233f0826300d8","tid":1784432,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"其實要停聖誕消費借黑警手係咪易過借火，一堆人唱吓歌都發癲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:12:29.000Z","msg":"過年了，要出番多D 加班費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"黑警過肥年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 商家佬就執柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dacf5959ba0ee4f7c423029f9fa4ccff2351ee2c","tid":1784432,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"將軍澳、香港的不夜城<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f31e84d45ac06cdcfefcfb0aa96fcbbb2ed69d","tid":1784432,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:18:59.000Z","msg":"今日出街見到勁多人消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89130e161c2350265f362bc85f010edbc9de241d","tid":1784432,"uid":291603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T16:33:43.000Z","msg":"真心覺得外國人根本唔care香港嘅狀況<br />\n人哋食花生咁睇<br />\n自己香港自己救"}]}